title: Warbots Multiplayer v1.2 + secrets
description:
Highly competitive free PvP fighting game. Challenge friends to a 1v1 duel!

Warbots is an action-packed free PvP fighting game. Compete and rise in the Warbots worldwide league ranking! Challenge friends to a 1v1 duel using the real-time multiplayer!

You loved popping those mean pigs with your angry birds :). See if you do just as well now that the pigs respond in kind!
